...just coz!

Compilation of ~90 demos rolled up into one !FAKER! style.
(...if only I knew how to combine/load one after the other)


Done Sep 2025 to May 2026 by Dave, Claude and spaztic Copilot.
Made entirely with :
 -x32 Win 7, 
 -Notepad, 
 -Pasmo & SJasm with RBINARY, 
 -Paint Shop Pro 7.
 -16bit STEP grfx RAW2INC conversion utils for 128x64 and 256x192
 -File Manager from Win NT4.

Grok was trialled and got the boot.
Raw ChatGPT itself was not ever used. 
ChatGPT_Codex doesn't run on Win7.





